name: PS-11. Fermat`s Spiral Delaunay
description:
v4W.ENko - ""PS-11. Fermat`s Spiral Delaunay "". The Fermat`s Spiral algorithm is used to rotate points around the center of the image. This is continuation of the "Pattern Standardization" series which shows the usual "Fermat`s Spiral" approach. Grey rectangles are linked to the points of "Fermat`s Spiral" algorithm. The white lines are generated with "Delaunay triangulation" and are connecting the "Fermat`s Spiral" control points. 
Packed as GIF. 1024*1024px / 180 frames.
